Hoist was successful as the small compartment opened, howeve he had lost
his grip, and was sent flying from the momentum built up by the
thrashing of Sludge's head. He landed a bit away, but was determined. "I
am trying to fix you of your headache Sludge." Hoist groaned, sitting
up, using his one hand for support.
